# Rule: Tailwind Color Tokens Only

- **ID:** react19-tailwind-colors
- **Scope:** src/**/*.tsx, src/**/*.jsx, src/**/*.css, src/**/*.less
- **Description:**  
  Enforce using ONLY Tailwind color utilities. No hardcoded colors anywhere.
  ❌ No hardcoded hex colors `#a25772` anywhere
  ❌ No inline color styles `style={{ color: '#...' }}`  
  ❌ No CSS color declarations
  ✅ Use Tailwind color utilities with clsx for dynamic colors

## Checks

### ❌ Hardcoded hex colors (anywhere)
- Pattern: `#[0-9a-fA-F]{3,6}`
- Message: "NEVER use hardcoded hex colors. Use Tailwind color utilities instead."
- Severity: error

### ❌ Inline color styles  
- Pattern: `style={{.*color.*}}`
- Message: "Do not use inline color styles. Use Tailwind color utilities with clsx instead."
- Severity: error

### ❌ CSS color properties
- Pattern: `color:|background-color:|border-color:`
- Where: `*.css, *.less, *.scss`
- Message: "Do not set colors in CSS. Use Tailwind color utilities instead."
- Severity: error

### ✅ PinCap Brand Colors (Recommended)
- `text-rose-600` → Primary brand color (#a25772)
- `bg-rose-600` → Primary background
- `border-rose-600` → Primary border
- `text-pink-600` → Secondary color (#d42364)
- `bg-pink-600` → Secondary background
- `text-pink-400` → Accent color (#ec4899)
- `bg-gray-50` → Light background
- `text-gray-600` → Body text
- `border-gray-200` → Light border

### ✅ CSS Custom Properties (Alternative)
- `text-[var(--primary)]` → CSS custom property
- `bg-[var(--secondary)]` → CSS custom property
- `border-[var(--border)]` → CSS custom property
